Safari is the new kid on the block. Extremely fast, extremely powerful, and extremely driven to win. Safari is a fan of the site and has studied many matches before she stepped onto the mat. She is a master to be reckoned with.

Darling “The Grappler” is ranked 5th for a reason - she earned it. Every match she gets better and better. Darling is a style point whore. If she gets you in a hold, you will be molested fast and furious.

No one knew what to expect. No one knew we would have a real battle on our hands. No one knew that our 5th ranked wrestler would be tested to her limit by the newcomer Safari.

Lets just say this to tease you, the loser gets bound up and coerced to cum over and over with a vibrator until she begs the winner to stop. Real honest begging is so hot.
title: Darling "The Grappler" (8-4) vs Safari (0-0)
